* 1993 - ''[[Undertow (Tool album)|Undertow]]'' (2x Platinum, Zoo/BMG/Volcano: USA)
* 1996 - ''[[<U+00C6>nima]]'' (3x Platinum, Zoo/BMG/Volcano: USA)
* 2001 - ''[[Lateralus]]'' (2x Platinum, Volcano II/Tool Dissectional: USA)
* 2006 - ''[[10,000 Days]]'' (Platinum, Volcano II/Tool Dissectional: USA)
===Others===
* 1991 - ''[[Tool (album)|Tool]]'' a.k.a. ''72826'' demo (Toolshed)
* 1992 - ''[[Opiate (album)|Opiate]]'' EP (Platinum, Zoo/BMG/Volcano: USA)
* 2000 - ''[[Salival|Salival]]'' box set (Volcano II/Tool Dissectional: USA)

